%^CYAN%^BOLD%^SURVIVOR%^RESET%^

You are capable of surviving in harsh environments and enduring deadly assaults. You recognize the power of he body's ability to overcome even the most deadly of afflictions.

%^BOLD%^Trance:%^RESET%^
Skill Bonus : Survival
Trance Bonus : Damage Resistance, Fire Resistance, Cold Resistance

%^BOLD%^Maneuver:%^RESET%^
Spend psionic focus to gain a temporary will save bonus

